        "username": "William_Kelley",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/william_kelley/{size}/2314_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-06-14T22:22:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Ed Steinway\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Ed Steinway:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Excellent article, thank you for sharing Wes.</p>\n<p>Mr. Kelley, the geological background descriptions/history of the area was fascinating to read! One quick question for you \u2013 the 4th to last tasting note shows 1994 in the Title, but 1992 in the description. Was it the 1994 that you tasted?</p>\n<p>Thanks,<br>\nEd</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Ed, well spotted! It was the 1992 I tasted, I\u2019ve corrected the note accordingly. Thanks for pointing that out, and for your kind words.</p>\n<p>All best,</p>\n<p>William.</p>",
